VulnClaw
=======

VulnClaw is a derivative work that combines two MIT-licensed projects:

  Vulnbot  — Copyright (c) 2026 UncleC
              https://github.com/Unclecheng-li/Vulnbot

  HackBot   — Copyright (c) 2026 HackBot Team (Yashab Alam)
              https://github.com/yashab-cyber/hackbot

VulnClaw uses Vulnbot as its base (agent core, MCP toolchain, skills,
CLI/TUI/web surfaces) and ports selected intelligence modules from HackBot
(CVE, OSINT, topology, compliance/MITRE, findings scoring, remediation, and
PDF reporting).

